					</h1>
					<p class="text-lg md:text-xl lg:text-2xl text-gray-300 mb-8 max-w-3xl mx-auto" 
						data-aos="fade-up" 
						data-aos-delay="200">
						Discover our comprehensive suite of tools and resources designed to develop students' non-cognitive skills and drive academic success.
					</p>
					<div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-center items-center space-y-4 md:space-y-0 md:space-x-6"
